Text: Great stuff - good upload! In the future, label your torrent file with the models name - it makes everything easier to find instead of having it labeled 1st, 2nd.  For those that collect these and seed, this is a big help!  Thx for sharing.

Thanks for the tip, brnblnk.  I thought I DID rename those files, but apparently they're STILL showing up as "1st" and "2nd".  Sheesh.  Oh, well -- everyone will just have to rename the Kylie folders at their end.  Will be more careful in future.
